snippet.title: The Most Wanted Bandito
snippet.description: The Most Wanted Bandito Action game. Get on your horse and stay on track as long as you can robbing along.

snippet.title: Ninja Painter 2
snippet.description: Ninja Painter 2 Puzzle game. Move through the levels and try to paint the stated areas with the right color.

snippet.title: Ghosted
snippet.description: Ghosted Puzzle game. Help the ghost to pick up all stars and reach the exit of each challenging level.

snippet.title: Fear Unlimited
snippet.description: Fear Unlimited Help Encon, the master of slaughter to rebel against the undead and slay all the evil soldiers.

snippet.title: Fear Unlimited 2: Issue 1
snippet.description: Fear Unlimited 2: Issue 1 Kill as many enemies as you can and do it in the most stylish way as possible.

snippet.title: Treasure Seas Incorporated
snippet.description: Treasure Seas Incorporated Use your upgradeable submarine to hunt for treasures. Beware the dangerous sharks!

snippet.title: Wakeskate Invited
snippet.description: Wakeskate Invited 3D wakeskating game. Get some air and show of your kickflips, ollies, 360's and other slick tricks.

snippet.title: Hobo 3: Wanted
snippet.description: Hobo 3: Wanted Side scrolling fighting game. Use filthy fighting techniques to beat up the cops and stay out of prison.

snippet.title: The Enchanted Cave
snippet.description: The Enchanted Cave Role playing game with lots of weapons, spells, artifacts and monsters. Get to floor 100 of the cave.

snippet.title: Robin Hood: Twisted Tale
snippet.description: Robin Hood: Twisted Tale Interactive storybook with multiple endings. Spot the differences to continue the story.
